
>\project\src>pipenv install --ignore-pipfile
__________________________________________________

VIRUTALENV IN PYTHON:

\project>pipenv install [package names]

Nota: 'ejmp:  \project>pipenv install venv'

>\project\venv\Scripts>activate

Nota: 'ejmp: \project\venv\Scripts>activate/deactivate '

>\project\venv\Scripts>pipenv shell

... Nota: (Para salir del entorno virtual, puedes executar simplement exit, desde tu terminal.

(Scripts-uFinIKPs) (venv) C:\Users\brian\Desktop\flask-fix-py\venv\Scripts>exit

..... Esto desactivará el entorno y regresarás al entorno global. y en cuanto a volver activarlo tan solo vuelve a tipear pipenv shell.)

Nota: para isntalar cualquier modulo o paquete: 
(Scripts-uFinIKPs) (venv) C:\Users\brian\Desktop\flask-fix-py\venv\Scripts>pipenv install <package>

(Scripts-uFinIKPs) (venv) C:\Users\brian\Desktop\flask-fix-py\venv\Scripts>pipenv install  --python==3.6.10

(Scripts-uFinIKPs) (venv) C:\Users\brian\Desktop\flask-fix-py\venv\Scripts>pipenv install pip python requests==3.6.10

(Scripts-uFinIKPs) (venv) C:\Users\brian\Desktop\flask-fix-py\venv\Scripts>pipenv install flask

(Scripts-uFinIKPs) (venv) C:\Users\brian\Desktop\flask-fix-py\venv\Scripts>pipenv install gunicorn

(Scripts-uFinIKPs) (venv) C:\Users\brian\Desktop\flask-fix-py\venv\Scripts>

(Scripts-uFinIKPs) (venv) C:\Users\brian\Desktop\flask-fix-py\venv\Scripts>pipenv --help

(Scripts-uFinIKPs) (venv) C:\Users\brian\Desktop\flask-fix-py\venv\Scripts>pipenv run pip freeze

(Scripts-uFinIKPs) (venv) C:\Users\brian\Desktop\flask-fix-py\venv\Scripts>pipenv install pip freeze > ../../src/requirements.txt

(Scripts-uFinIKPs) (venv) C:\Users\brian\Desktop\flask-fix-py\venv\Scripts>pipenv install flask --dev

(Scripts-uFinIKPs) (venv) C:\Users\brian\Desktop\flask-fix-py\venv\Scripts>pipenv graph

(Scripts-uFinIKPs) (venv) C:\Users\brian\Desktop\flask-fix-py\venv\Scripts>pipenv install flask --dev
